67657E99.Line3.11EA17: I'm sorry, stranger. You must have better things to do with your time than hear of a parent's disappointment in their child. Thank you for returning him to me.

8EE1D4D7.Line1.11EA17: Good. Good. (sigh) That boy. He never should have gone to Guulrahn. I wanted him to take over the farm, but he had dreams of making it big.
